data.description: Discover this beautiful and cozy home nestled in Taft, complete with a newer HVAC unit and classic charm. Offering 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a versatile bonus space that can easily become a 3rd bedroom, this property is a true gem.  Inside, you'll find a functional floor plan that welcomes  natural light. The kitchen is a highlight, boasting ample storage and generous counter space. Step outside to a serene pool and a covered patio sitting area, perfect for unwinding and hosting gatherings. Conveniently located near shopping, parks and schools, this inviting property is the perfect blend of modern living and comfort. A dream home waiting for you to call it yours! Schedule your showing today!
